			<h3>Who, what, where, and when?</h3>
			<div><em>(To select multiple options, hold down the shift key.<br>All fields must have at least one selection.)</em>
			</div>
			<br>
				<%= form_tag(results_path, :method => "get", id: "param_search") do %>
